 Precision Spindle & Accessories Inc.Products & Services

Spindle Repair ServicesOur spindle repair service facility offers repair, rebuild, recondition, refurbish and rework.
Coolant CoolersMachine tool coolant coolers for coolant sumps, coolant filtration systems and cutting oils.
Chucks Repair & RebuildOur workholding partner manufactures standard, special and custom power chucks, manual chucks and collet chucks.
Ball Screw RepairStandard and custom ballscrew repair, special ball screw repair, reball, recirculating ball screw assembly repair services.
Spindle BearingsOur partners supply precision machine tool spindle bearings, seals and o-rings.
